  "notes": [
    "Canonical upstream URIs, extracted from broadinstitute/gatk-sv@7eb2af1feea9",
    "inputs/values/resources_hg38.json. Mixes two public GCS buckets:",
    "  gs://gcp-public-data--broad-references/ (primary reference files)",
    "  gs://gatk-sv-resources-public/           (SV-specific panels and tracks)",
    "",
    "Broad also mirrors the primary reference files under the public-requester-pays",
    "bucket s3://broad-references/hg38/v0/ (same file names). Because that mirror",
    "is in us-east-1, cross-region copy via boto3 s3.copy is fine for",
    "intra-AWS staging and avoids egress costs on reruns.",
    "",
    "expected_md5/expected_sha256 are left null until we compute them post-stage.",
    "Until then the stager copies without checksum verification; fill them in",
    "after the first successful stage for regression pinning."
  ],
